description:
My HoneyDew this week is Steve Simeone! Steve returns to The Dew to talk about what a terrible athlete he was and The HoneyDew of all roommates, Fat James! This is such a fun ep with so many laughs!

Make sure you subscribe to my YouTube channel & be ready to watch The Dew there next toozdee, June 2nd!
